  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Echoes of Spellcraft</strong></i> is a single-player game that combines the strategic depth of roguelike deck-building with the thrill of real-time dynamic combat. Play powerful spells at the right moment, encounter different events, and adopt unique strategies in each game to defeat endless waves of enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/b8d4f4abb876380f86a0ccaf7704c314.avif?t=1750736224\" width=491 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/581e8fed9e7c83faf4fdb2f8bffd1eaf.webp?t=1750736224\" width=560 height=63 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist automatically seeks out and attacks the nearest enemy.  <br>All you need to do is drag and drop spells at the right moments to unleash them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/a181cfcb54e0655bf3d08e27c59cf2d2.poster.avif?t=1750736224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/a181cfcb54e0655bf3d08e27c59cf2d2.webm?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/a181cfcb54e0655bf3d08e27c59cf2d2.mp4?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/a2ca5d3b27b00206e9c5e67d70674403.webp?t=1750736224\" width=560 height=63 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Casting spells increases your Heat, which will gradually decrease over time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But be careful—casting too many spells will lead to Overload, preventing you from casting any spells until fully cooled down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/f3d3830c702440a86dec242804ea41be.poster.avif?t=1750736224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/f3d3830c702440a86dec242804ea41be.webm?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/f3d3830c702440a86dec242804ea41be.mp4?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/8b19035756c2cfe4561da50e2df73c08.webp?t=1750736224\" width=560 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Treasure, shops, facing elite monsters, or exploring the unknown—the choice is yours.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/928eb3f6a5d4cb146149a2566bae689d.poster.avif?t=1750736224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/928eb3f6a5d4cb146149a2566bae689d.webm?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/928eb3f6a5d4cb146149a2566bae689d.mp4?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/70c84efbe1b3fa25ea689988764dc66d.webp?t=1750736224\" width=560 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Synthesize basic spells into higher-level ones, or maintain specific spell combinations to trigger additional synergy effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/6ea8cc6d7de7fe7f225c2df021cc0b98.poster.avif?t=1750736224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/6ea8cc6d7de7fe7f225c2df021cc0b98.webm?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/6ea8cc6d7de7fe7f225c2df021cc0b98.mp4?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/08c2a8e367bdade29b239a3351f32ed3.webp?t=1750736224\" width=560 height=63 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ meticulously designed spells, 50+ unique enemies, 8 different hero abilities, along with various events and relics are all waiting for you to explore!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/eabe4c5a5389eb2baafd5b9eb1a127c2.poster.avif?t=1750736224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/eabe4c5a5389eb2baafd5b9eb1a127c2.webm?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/eabe4c5a5389eb2baafd5b9eb1a127c2.mp4?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Echoes of Spellcraft</strong></i> is a single-player game that combines the strategic depth of roguelike deck-building with the thrill of real-time dynamic combat. Play powerful spells at the right moment, encounter different events, and adopt unique strategies in each game to defeat endless waves of enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/b8d4f4abb876380f86a0ccaf7704c314.avif?t=1750736224\" width=491 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/581e8fed9e7c83faf4fdb2f8bffd1eaf.webp?t=1750736224\" width=560 height=63 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist automatically seeks out and attacks the nearest enemy.  <br>All you need to do is drag and drop spells at the right moments to unleash them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/a181cfcb54e0655bf3d08e27c59cf2d2.poster.avif?t=1750736224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/a181cfcb54e0655bf3d08e27c59cf2d2.webm?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/a181cfcb54e0655bf3d08e27c59cf2d2.mp4?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/a2ca5d3b27b00206e9c5e67d70674403.webp?t=1750736224\" width=560 height=63 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Casting spells increases your Heat, which will gradually decrease over time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But be careful—casting too many spells will lead to Overload, preventing you from casting any spells until fully cooled down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/f3d3830c702440a86dec242804ea41be.poster.avif?t=1750736224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/f3d3830c702440a86dec242804ea41be.webm?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/f3d3830c702440a86dec242804ea41be.mp4?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/8b19035756c2cfe4561da50e2df73c08.webp?t=1750736224\" width=560 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Treasure, shops, facing elite monsters, or exploring the unknown—the choice is yours.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/928eb3f6a5d4cb146149a2566bae689d.poster.avif?t=1750736224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/928eb3f6a5d4cb146149a2566bae689d.webm?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/928eb3f6a5d4cb146149a2566bae689d.mp4?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/70c84efbe1b3fa25ea689988764dc66d.webp?t=1750736224\" width=560 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Synthesize basic spells into higher-level ones, or maintain specific spell combinations to trigger additional synergy effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/6ea8cc6d7de7fe7f225c2df021cc0b98.poster.avif?t=1750736224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/6ea8cc6d7de7fe7f225c2df021cc0b98.webm?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/6ea8cc6d7de7fe7f225c2df021cc0b98.mp4?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/08c2a8e367bdade29b239a3351f32ed3.webp?t=1750736224\" width=560 height=63 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ meticulously designed spells, 50+ unique enemies, 8 different hero abilities, along with various events and relics are all waiting for you to explore!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/eabe4c5a5389eb2baafd5b9eb1a127c2.poster.avif?t=1750736224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asset